highlights.text: “Die With A Smile” by Lady Gaga and Bruno Mars has been on Top Songs Norway the longest, at 385 days straight.
Ari Bajgora has the most spots on Top Songs Norway. “Falle og slå seg” is the highest at #3.
“Ælsk nånn” by Ingrid Vårvik is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Norway, up 47 spots at #91.
“Predador de Perereca” by BLOW RECORDS and Mc Jhey is the highest new entry on Top Songs Norway at #143.
